  "title": "Rich Roasted Mexican Broccoli Chiles Rellenos",
  "description": "A rich and cheesy Mexican dish featuring roasted purple sprouting broccoli and poblano peppers, perfect for a hangover cure. This dish is gluten-free friendly and offers a delicious cheese-pull experience.",
