  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Roast the poblano peppers in the oven for 30 minutes, then peel and chop them.",
    "Steam the purple sprouting broccoli until tender, then set aside.",
    "In a pan, saute the onion and garlic until softened.",
    "In a bowl, mix the queso fresco, egg, and cream.",
    "Stuff each poblano pepper with the cheese mixture, then coat with the beaten egg.",
    "Roll the stuffed peppers in the steamed broccoli, then place on a baking dish.",
    "Bake the chiles rellenos in the oven for 20 minutes, or until golden brown.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste, then serve hot."
